	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. Load SCL_Main_A.&#xD;&#xA;2. Go to -8; 28; 119.&#xD;&#xA;3. Approach the checkpoint.&#xD;&#xA;4. Start the checkpoint dialogue.&#xD;&#xA;5. Continue through the checkpoint dialogue without antagonising Jaheira.&#xD;&#xA;6. Continue to -65; 31; 157&#xD;&#xA;7. Talk to Marcus.&#xD;&#xA;8. In the dialogue with Marcus, don't antagonise him.&#xD;&#xA;9. Continue onto the balcony.&#xD;&#xA;10. Talk to Isobel.&#xD;&#xA;11, End the dialogue with Isobel.&#xD;&#xA;12. Dialogue between Isobel and Marcus begins.&#xD;&#xA;13. Finish dialogue, enter combat.&#xD;&#xA;14. In combat, kill or incapacitate Marcus, while he is in line of sight of Isobel." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="1" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Marcus is defeated after having betrayed Isobel." />
